{"tid":2398024,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友唔想要BB, 應唔應該飛左佢","createTime":"2021-02-07T02:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T08:04:29.000Z","uid":127425,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"38b37bd1108beb6745f5ec9e18b62a3a59d69492","tid":2398024,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:54:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我地一開始係埋一齊係唔想要BB既<br />\n想一直二人世界<br />\n但係同佢相處耐左<br />\n就想生番個<br />\n我知你地會屌我話女人好善變<br />\n不過我真係好想有自己家庭<br />\n但係男朋友死都唔想生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應唔應該搵過另一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7ef95a6773da17ce857e683f3388fe82e7b313","tid":2398024,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"應該"},{"pid":"2a1453940685d4f19d225fe27f80c79e3e042b35","tid":2398024,"uid":54387,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:55:48.000Z","msg":"感建分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真，唔好害你男朋友"},{"pid":"8ff7da1f3787d422fb35eed097f6fef8f7631c04","tid":2398024,"uid":277296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a9c5dc00d4cd659242dfe31a0aeafe5c7263b9","tid":2398024,"uid":374180,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1aHU0Ba.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1aHU0Ba.gif&h=62802a7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bec9e0167ae400a0bf892eb12b654a67eb40fe9b","tid":2398024,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:59:42.000Z","msg":"This"},{"pid":"f70481c01d550084776c05379d6652102fc88cdb","tid":2398024,"uid":42250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"我同你生, 比返小小補品費就ok"},{"pid":"dded8d65f78c266331139d646d9fbd569babe387","tid":2398024,"uid":127955,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:01:10.000Z","msg":"生定唔生係任何couple最首要有共識的事情。<br />\n都唔理經濟呀，生活夾唔夾，未來光唔光明之類。<br />\n<br />\n因為呢樣野，唔係講緊遷唔遷就，假如佢遷就左你要生，佢都唔會有心湊。最後好多argue，彈一句係氣要生咋嘛又唔係我。<br />\n<br />\n但反之你唔生就一生遺憾。人生冇左一部分。<br />\n<br />\n如果仲後生就算罷啦，next."},{"pid":"97b511741d7b746fd7f3390bb9f2165844381cf3","tid":2398024,"uid":282362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:01:57.000Z","msg":"男人係唔會有bb"},{"pid":"f7837862076a4a5f31a70d75480b3e56424d1ebf","tid":2398024,"uid":33939,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">不過我真係好想有自己家庭</span><br />\n<br />\n你好想？有冇諗過對方唔想？我係指你嘅仔女跟本唔想出世，有冇諗過佢生活得唔開心，跟住問你點解要生佢出嚟？咁你點答？答佢因為生你出嚟就可以滿足到自己想有家庭嘅慾望？問題係佢唔想有你哩個家庭喎！咁想要家庭不如去露宿者之家吖！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">btw，男人同男人點生仔？</span>"},{"pid":"d695c65663b888233765e0e9a86719f360cd4232","tid":2398024,"uid":351787,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:03:47.000Z","msg":"生，唔得既搵人借種，唔好落入老鼠烏托邦嘅陷阱"},{"pid":"33db48dd1462f905e684c1791f39e5f6a59a6767","tid":2398024,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f7837862076a4a5f31a70d75480b3e56424d1ebf","tid":2398024,"uid":33939,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">不過我真係好想有自己家庭</span><br />\n<br />\n你好想？有冇諗過對方唔想？我係指你嘅仔女跟本唔想出世，有冇諗過佢生活得唔開心，跟住問你點解要生佢出嚟？咁你點答？答佢因為生你出嚟就可以滿足到自己想有家庭嘅慾望？問題係佢唔想有你哩個家庭喎！咁想要家庭不如去露宿者之家吖！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">btw，男人同男人點生仔？</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi